=== Tunl

Creates ssh tunnels on EC2

=== INSTALL

- install dependencies:
	sudo gem install thor
	sudo gem install right_aws

- run rake install to install the gem
- create the tunl root directory ~/.tunl
  the tunl root directory will store aws params and ssh key pair's
- create the tunl config file: ~/.tunl/tunl.yml and set your aws params


=== USAGE

execute tunl -h for usage instructions

